<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.1">
<l>ciṉavilceṅ kaṇarak karuyir māḷac ceṟṟavilli yeṉṟukaṟṟa vartantam</l>
<l>maṉamuṭkoṇ ṭeṉṟumep pōtuniṉ ṟēttum māmuṉiyai maramēḻey tamaintaṉai</l>
<l>naṉavilceṉ ṟārkkumnaṇ ṇaṟkariyā ṉainā ṉaṭiyēṉ naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampiyai</l>
<l>kaṉavilkaṇ ṭēṉiṉṟu kaṇṭamaiyā leṉkaṇ ṇiṇaikaḷ kaḷippak kaḷittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, his servant, saw in a dream the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">the great sage whom each scholar praises every day, always,</l>
<l>Continually taking [him] into his heart, saying</l>
<l rend="indent">“Bowman who, without anger, tormented the demons</l>
<l>With red eyes, so that [their] lives ended,”</l>
<l rend="indent">the youth who shot seven trees,</l>
<l>The one who is difficult to reach for even those who approach in wakefulness;</l>
<l rend="indent">now since both of my eyes rejoiced by seeing [him],</l>
<l>I rejoiced.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
